item.title: Star Craft 2 BETA omgomgomgomgomg
item.dc:creator: @repacsenur repacsenur
item.description:
@repacsenur wrote:

WARNING!!!

I installed this Beta a few weeks back, tried to log into battle.net, tried the lazy launcher and nothing worked. So I just uninstalled everything and carried on. Last Friday I received a notice from Blizzard that my WoW account (which I have not even accessed in more than a year) had been closed. Turns out someone hijacked my account and tried to sell it for money.

I CANNOT THINK OF ANY OTHER WAY THAT SOMETHING LIKE THIS COULD HAPPEN! This has been the first time I have logged into my battle.net account in over a year. Plus, judging from a previous user’s comment, this cannot be a coincidence. Just be careful guys!

something to think when downloading those cracks these people keylog everything ;D to profit
